    "(5) Page 11 of 62 19",
    "The CycleGAN is trained using the objective function defined in Eq. 8.",
    "5, 6, 7, and 8 are reported from Singh and Raza (2021).",
    "DiscoGAN is another unsupervised GAN variant used for image-to-image translation tasks, but it focuses on discovering cross-domain relations between two distinct domains (Kim et al. 2017).",
    "The main goal of DiscoGAN is to learn the cross-domain relationships between two unpaired datasets, without using any paired data during the training process."
